track_notes: Nice walk. Several parking spaces on minor road. Follow river and waterfalls up to plateau and then cross to Llyn Fan Fawr. Easy to follow path from here up the escarpment to the summit.

Total time (including ops): 3hr 30m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T2. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
